t\'s clean and doesn\'t require any changes to the existing `StatisticsTab`. I\'m going to rewrite `src/App.tsx` completely to support the full flow. I\'m excited about the new login block, the top bar with a logout button for easy role switching (C\303\241n b\341\273\231 nh\341\272\255p li\341\273\207u, etc.), and integrated CRUD actions for `periods` and `criteria`!\n\n\n**Updating Header Functionality**\n\nI\'m now revising `Header.tsx` to handle dynamic user data. I\'ll integrate the `UserSession` details directly into the header for a personalized display, and add a \"\304\220\304\203ng xu\341\272\245t\" button for easy logouts. I\'m focusing on making sure the logout triggers the correct state updates across the app.\n\n\n"
