  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Confirming Success and Scope**\n\nI\'m thrilled; both the linting and build phases completed flawlessly! Now, I\'m doing a quick review, cross-referencing the initial user requirements with the successful outcomes to ensure everything aligns perfectly. I\'m focusing on \"Ng\306\260\341\273\235i d\303\271ng \304\221\304\203ng nh\341\272\255p --> Dashboard -->\" specifically, and confirming it is fully addressed.\n\n\n**Visualizing Workflow Implementation**\n\nI\'ve mapped out the navigation flow: \"Criteria Category\" with CRUD, \"Reporting Periods\" with CRUD, and viewing period details like NTM reports with 04-13 forms. I\'m focusing on the user journey from viewing form details to report submission, validation, and supervision. The UI upgrades look amazing, with polished national navy and gold elements, glowing badges, glassmorphism, dynamic notifications, and premium charts.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "T\303\264i \304\221\303\243 ho\303\240n thi\341\273\207n to\303\240n di\341\273\207n t\341\272\245t c\341\272\243 c\303\241c ph\303\242n h\341\273\207 giao di\341\273\207n ng\306\260\341\273\235i d\303\271ng (UI/UX) theo ti\303\252u chu\341\272\251n qu\341\273\221c gia hi\341\273\207n \304\221\341\272\241i, sang tr\341\273\215ng, lo\341\272\241i b\341\273\217 ho\303\240n to\303\240n c\303\241c y\341\272\277u t\341\273\221 s\306\241 s\303\240i \304\221\341\273\203 mang l\341\272\241i tr\341\272\243i nghi\341\273\207m chuy\303\252n nghi\341\273\207p nh\341\272\245t:\n\n### \360\237\214\237 T\341\273\225ng quan N\303\242ng c\341\272\245p & T\303\255nh n\304\203ng H\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng\n\n1. **Giao di\341\273\207n \304\220\304\203ng nh\341\272\255p H\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng (`LoginScreen`)**:\n   - Kho\303\241c l\303\252n m\303\254nh giao di\341\273\207n **K\303\255nh m\341\273\235 (Glassmorphism)** k\341\272\277t h\341\273\243p gi\341\273\257a m\303\240u xanh Deep Corporate Navy \304\221\341\272\263ng c\341\272\245p v\303\240 c\303\241c chi ti\341\272\277t vi\341\273\201n nh\305\251 v\303\240ng sang tr\341\273\215ng.\n   - Qu\341\273\221c huy Vi\341\273\207t Nam \304\221\306\260\341\273\243c ph\341\273\221i m\303\240u n\341\273\225i b\341\272\255t c\303\271ng v\341\273\233i c\303\241c n\303\272t ch\341\273\215n nhanh t\303\240i kho\341\272\243n t\306\260\306\241ng \341\273\251ng v\341\273\233i c\303\241c vai tr\303\262 ng\306\260\341\273\235i d\303\271ng trong lu\341\273\223ng nghi\341\273\207p v\341\273\245.\n\n2. **Thanh \304\220i\341\273\201u h\306\260\341\273\233ng & Header (`Sidebar` & `Header`)**:\n   - Sidebar \304\221\306\260\341\273\243c thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 \304\221\341\273\223ng b\341\273\231 v\341\273\233i t\303\264ng m\303\240u xanh s\341\272\253m qu\303\275 ph\303\241i v\303\240 s\341\272\257c v\303\240ng \303\241nh kim, t\303\255ch h\341\273\243p hi\341\273\207u \341\273\251ng chuy\341\273\203n \304\221\341\273\231ng t\341\273\221i t\303\242n khi di chu\341\273\231t ch\341\273\215n c\303\241c ph\303\242n h\341\273\207.\n   - Header d\341\272\241ng K\303\255nh m\341\273\235 ph\341\273\247 n\341\273\201n, hi\341\273\203n th\341\273\213 th\303\264ng b\303\241o nghi\341\273\207p v\341\273\245 tr\341\273\261c quan theo th\341\273\235i gian th\341\273\261c c\303\271ng \303\264 t\303\254m ki\341\272\277m th\303\264ng minh m\341\273\237 r\341\273\231ng.\n\n3. **T\341\273\225ng quan Ph\303\242n t\303\255ch (`OverviewTab`)**:\n   - Banner c\341\273\225 \304\221\341\273\231ng thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 trang tr\341\273\215ng v\341\273\233i ho\341\272\241 ti\341\272\277t n\303\264ng nghi\341\273\207p ch\341\272\245t l\306\260\341\273\243ng cao l\341\273\223ng gh\303\251p chuy\341\273\203n \304\221\341\273\225i s\341\273\221.\n   - H\341\273\207 th\341\273\221ng bi\341\273\203u \304\221\341\273\223 ph\341\273\247 d\341\272\243i Gradient m\303\240u tinh t\341\272\277, hi\341\273\203n th\341\273\213 chi ti\341\272\277t ti\341\272\277n \304\221\341\273\231 ho\303\240n th\303\240nh ch\341\273\211 ti\303\252u c\341\273\247a t\341\273\253ng ph\303\242n v\303\271ng.\n\n4. **Qu\341\272\243n l\303\275 \304\220\341\273\243t B\303\241o c\303\241o (`ReportPeriodsTab`)**:\n   - To\303\240n b\341\273\231 danh s\303\241ch \304\221\341\273\243t \304\221\303\241nh gi\303\241 \304\221\306\260\341\273\243c c\341\272\245u tr\303\272c d\306\260\341\273\233i d\341\272\241ng th\341\272\273 b\303\240i sang tr\341\273\215ng c\303\263 t\303\255nh to\303\241n t\341\273\211 l\341\273\207 % ho\303\240n th\303\240nh \304\221\341\273\231ng, h\341\273\227 tr\341\273\243 \304\221\341\272\247y \304\221\341\273\247 c\303\241c t\303\255nh n\304\203ng Th\303\252m/S\341\273\255a/X\303\263a (CRUD) \304\221\341\273\243t r\303\240 so\303\241t.\n\n5. **Chi ti\341\272\277t Bi\341\273\203u m\341\272\253u & Quy tr\303\254nh Th\341\272\251m nghi\341\273\207p (`FormDetailView`)**:\n   - Giao di\341\273\207n b\341\272\243ng bi\341\273\203u thi\341\272\277t k\341\272\277 tinh x\341\272\243o, h\341\273\227 tr\341\273\243 t\303\255nh n\304\203ng **Ph\341\272\243n h\341\273\223i nh\341\272\245p nh\303\241y (Input Flash Feedback)** khi thay \304\221\341\273\225i s\341\273\221 li\341\273\207u.\n   - Quy tr\303\254nh **K\303\275 s\341\273\221 X\303\241c th\341\273\261c (X\303\241c th\341\273\261c ch\341\273\251ng th\306\260 s\341\273\221 CA)** v\341\273\233i popup k\303\275 s\341\273\221 ph\303\241p l\303\275 chuy\303\252n nghi\341\273\207p.\n   - Giao di\341\273\207n Th\341\272\251m \304\221\341\273\213nh c\341\272\245p t\341\273\211nh v\303\240 \304\220\303\263ng d\341\272\245u Gi\303\241m s\303\241t c\341\273\247a M\341\272\267t tr\341\272\255n T\341\273\225 qu\341\273\221c ph\341\273\221i m\303\240u ch\341\272\267t ch\341\272\275 \304\221\303\272ng v\341\273\233i lu\341\273\223ng nghi\341\273\207p v\341\273\245 li\303\252n ng\303\240nh.\n\n6. **S\341\273\225 tay Ti\303\252u ch\303\255 & Bi\341\273\203u \304\221\341\273\223 Th\341\273\221ng k\303\252 (`CriteriaTab` & `StatisticsTab`)**:\n   - Ph\303\242n h\341\273\207 S\341\273\225 tay Ti\303\252u chu\341\272\251n \304\221\306\260\341\273\243c l\303\240m m\341\273\233i ho\303\240n to\303\240n v\341\273\233i c\303\241c th\341\272\273 ch\341\273\211 ti\303\252u vi\341\273\201n m\341\273\235 cao c\341\272\245p, th\341\272\273 tr\341\273\215ng s\341\273\221 \303\241nh kim v\303\240 h\341\273\231p tho\341\272\241i h\341\273\227 tr\341\273\243 CRUD ti\303\252u chu\341\272\251n.\n   - Ph\303\242n h\341\273\207 Th\341\273\221ng k\303\252 n\303\242ng c\341\272\245p bi\341\273\203u \304\221\341\273\223 Recharts cao c\341\272\245p v\341\273\233i ch\303\272 th\303\255ch d\341\273\257 li\341\273\207u chu\341\272\251n h\303\263a v\303\240 t\303\255nh n\304\203ng xu\341\272\245t d\341\273\257 li\341\273\207u Excel t\341\273\251c th\341\273\235i."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 1
      nanos: 908866389
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
